text:
Hm? What's wrong Mikoto?
Is something written there bothering you?

No, it's not that...
I was just thinking how there's so much writing.

Stuff that's got nothing to do with work... like doodles and stuff────
283Pro really is different, huh.

Haha, no kidding.
Want to write something as well, Mikoto?

Sure, you should definitely write something.
You're also a member of 283Pro after all.
